<DOCNO>WT17-B07-45</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA057-000938-B016-4</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/townhall/columnists/fumento/fume030896.html 204.71.237.73 19970109105741 text/html 7257
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
