http://www.savers.org:80/townhall/columnists/aipe/smit080796.html 204.71.237.73 19970109133517 text/html 4576
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 13:35:36 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 12-Aug-96 13:51:25 GMT
