<P><TT><B><A NAME="51">51</A></B></TT>		No one knows what the future value
of  the dollar will be, especially far out into the future as is projected in
this number.  Over recent history, the dollar has dropped in  value by an
average of about 3 percent per annum. Hence, the value of these dollars will be 
considerably lower the further out the projection goes.
</P>
<P><B><TT><A NAME="52">52</A></TT></B>		From research on personal time
